|        |                                 |
|                                          |
|        +                                 |
|   ==   |                                 |
|        |                                 |
|        |                                 |
|   ==   +---------------------------------+

Horrible boss who asks for more money every day.
Final score = daily money + accumulated tip money
- cars come in between 7AM and 12PM
- cars leave between 4PM and 9PM
- if there is still a car at midnight, you're fired


